  "text": "We will show that the variance of these Beta variables is of order n \u22121 . To concisely describe the integrand that results in the limit, put \u03c4 to be the variable over which the integral is taken, and define e(\u03c4 ) and e \u2032 (\u03c4 ) as [CITATION_1] e(\u03c4 ) := b \u2212 a + 2a\u03c4 1 \u2212 2a + 2a\u03c4 and e \u2032 (\u03c4 ) :",
